OL,3,CTwo men arrested after girl, 9, killed
OL,4,Cin two-car collision
OL,6,FA nine-year-old girl has died after a
OL,7,Ftwo-car crash in Birmingham.
OL,9,FPolice were called to Icknield Street
OL,10,Fin the Hockley area of the city, at
OL,11,Faround 11pm on Thursday 2nd April.
OL,13,FThe girl was a passenger in one of two
OL,14,Fcars involved in the collision.
OL,16,FShe was taken to hospital with serious
OL,17,Finjuries, but died soon after.
