OL,3,CTwo men arrested after girl, 9, killed
OL,4,Cin two-car collision
OL,6,FTwo men have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of drug-driving and on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,9,Fdangerous driving.
OL,11,F"Our thoughts are with her loved ones"
OL,13,FA statement issued by West Midlands
OL,14,FPolice said:
OL,16,F"Our thoughts are with her loved ones
OL,17,Fat this devastating time.
OL,19,F"A woman and two other children from
OL,20,Fthe same car were also taken to
OL,21,Fhospital to be assessed for injuries.
