OL,3,CTwo men arrested after girl, 9, killed
OL,4,Cin two-car collision
OL,6,F"Two men aged 22 and 23 from the
OL,7,Fsecond car, a BMW, have been arrested
OL,8,Fon suspicion of causing death by
OL,9,Fdangerous driving and driving whilst
OL,10,Funfit through drugs."
OL,12,FPolice are appealing for any witnesses
OL,13,For anyone with relevant dashcam or
OL,14,Fdoorbell footage to contact them.
